        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 71876,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Dado que la autoasignación es una herramienta poderosa para construir programas, aprendamos algunos operadores que nos ayudan a escribir código más rápido.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Intro 2",
            "id": 71882,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Sabemos que podemos sumar <code>1</code> a una variable escribiendo el nombre de la variable. En este caso, <code>likes</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" likes = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"likes = likes + \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(likes);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"28\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"6\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>likes</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "+= operator",
            "id": 71877,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>En lugar de reescribir el nombre de la variable, podemos usar el operador <code>+=</code> para sumar un número con <code>likes += 1</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" likes = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"likes += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(likes);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"20\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"25\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"6\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>likes</code> seguido de <code>+=</code> y finalmente <code>1</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "-= operator",
            "id": 71878,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para restar del valor de una variable, usamos el operador <code>-=</code>, como aquí donde disminuimos <code>likes</code> en <code>3</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" likes = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"likes -= \" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(likes);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"23\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"2\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>-=</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "++ operator",
            "id": 72161,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>El <strong>operador de incremento</strong>, <code>++</code>, colocado después del nombre de una variable, aumenta su valor en <code>1</code>. Aquí, <code>likes++</code> aumentará el valor de <code>5</code> a <code>6</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" likes = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"likes++;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(likes);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"20\" /><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"21\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"22\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"6\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>likes</code> seguido de <code>+</code> y finalmente <code>+</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "-- operator",
            "id": 72162,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos restar <code>1</code> del valor de una variable usando el <strong>operador de decremento</strong> ( <code>--</code> ) tal como aquí con <code>likes--</code> .</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" likes = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"likes--;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(likes);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"likes++\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"4\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>likes--</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: += operator",
            "id": 72153,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Qué muestra este código en la consola?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" marbles = \" /><text value=\"6\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"marbles += \" /><text value=\"2\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(marbles);\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"8\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>8</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>6</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>8</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: -= operator",
            "id": 72154,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Qué operador usamos para restar un número del valor de una variable?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>-=</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>+=</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>-=</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Incrementing numbers",
            "id": 72155,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Qué operador suma uno al valor de una variable?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>++</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>--</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>++</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Decrementing numbers",
            "id": 72156,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Qué muestra este código en la consola?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" speed = \" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"speed--;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(speed);\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"199\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>199</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>201</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>199</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: += operator",
            "id": 72159,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Agrega diez al valor de la variable usando el operador <code>+=</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" yards = \" /><text value=\"80\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"yards += \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(yards);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"21\" /><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"24\" /><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"27\" /><option startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"28\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"90\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>yards</code> seguido de <code>+</code> y luego <code>=</code>, <code>10</code>, <code>;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: -= operator",
            "id": 72160,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Resta 200 del valor de la variable usando el operador <code>-=</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" account = \" /><text value=\"1000\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"account -= \" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(account);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option startIndex=\"28\" endIndex=\"30\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"800\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>-=</code> seguido de <code>200</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
